BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:77B7_Y_nmocHW8IMKYSX7
SUMMARY:Kenyon Hall's Pocket Sessions
DTSTAMP:20260403T032252Z
DTSTART:20260408T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:KENYON HALL PRESENTS\n\nPocket Sessions\n\nFirst Tuesday of Eve
	ry Month Tuesday\, April 7th\, 2026 Doors and Signup: 6:30pm\n\nAll Ages S
	eated FREE ENTRY\n\nThe Kenyon Hall Quartet Featuring sounds from: Tige De
	Coster- upright bass Tim Kennedy -keys and wurlitzer Nik Jordan- guitar oL
	Li kLoMp- drums/mc\n\nDJ westwood- vinyl moods\n\nPocket Sessions is Kenyo
	n Hall’s first ever FREE instrumental jamm session! Vibes\, improvisation\
	, spur of the moment creation\, and good times. Come join us\, bring your 
