DESCRIPTION:Description Have you been putting off your taxes? Want someone 
	to do them for you for free? We got you!Join us on April 10 from 2-8 pm at
	 the Minority Vets Community for our Free Tax Clinic in partnership with U
	nited Way of King County. Must live in WA state\; most income types are el
	igible. Details can be found at the registration link. Please share with y
	our loved ones! All in the community are welcome\; you do not need to be a
	 veteran to attend.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free-
